    <h2 class="section--heading">Payment</h2>
    <div class="faqs-section">
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">
          Payment for the order has been deducted from my account, but no order
          details have been received?
        </p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            You order details may have not been captured with us. The amount
            will be refunded to your account in next 5-7 days.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">What payment options do you have?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Keeping in mind the health and safety in these times, we accept
            prepaid orders only to minimize the contact. You can choose to pay
            by the following options:
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li>Credit/Debit Card Payment</li>
            <li>Net Banking</li>
            <li>Wallets – PhonePe, Amazon Pay, FreeCharge, Payzapp</li>
            <li>UPI/QR</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="section--heading">Order Related</h2>
    <div class="faqs-section">
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">How can I cancel my order?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            You have the option to cancel your order before it is dispatched
            from our warehouse.<br /><br />

            To cancel the order: <br />
          </p>

          <p><strong>If you have an account:</strong></p>

          <ol>
            <li>Login to your account</li>
            <li>
              <span>Go to manage your order:</span>
              <a href="https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/apps/ret"
                >https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/apps/ret</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>Cancel the desired order.</li>
          </ol>

          <p>
            If you don’t have an account, create an account at
            <a href="https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/account/register"
              >https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/account/register</a
            >
            and follow the steps mentioned above.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">I want to change my delivery address?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>Before the order is dispatched:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Cancel the order on the website and place the order again with the
              correct address.
            </li>
            <li>
              Contact our customer care team to change the delivery address.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            <span>By Email:</span>
            <a href="mailto:info@imaginemarketingindia.com"
              >info@imaginemarketingindia.com</a
            >
            <br />
          </p>
          <p>
            <span>By Phone:</span>
            <a href="tel:912249461882">+912249461882</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            *Delivery address cannot be changed once the product has been
            dispatched from our warehouse.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">I want to change my product color?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Before the order is dispatched, cancel the order on the website and
            place the order again with the desired product colour.
          </p>

          <p>
            *Product Colour cannot be changed once the product has been
            dispatched from our warehouse.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">I have lost my invoice copy, what should I do?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <ul>
            <li>
              Order placed through Amazon/FK/Any other ecommerce marketplace:
              Locate your invoice in the order details of your account on the
              website from where you placed the order for boAt products.
            </li>
            <li>
              Order placed on the website: Contact Customer Service to help you.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="section--heading">Shipping</h2>
    <div class="faqs-section">
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">When can I expect the delivery of my product?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Once you receive the shipping confirmation, your package will be
            delivered within 3-5 business days. We are constantly working to get
            your order delivered as soon as possible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">How do I track my order details?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            An email and an SMS with the tracking number will be sent once the
            order has been dispatched from our warehouse. You can also track
            your order from your account on the website by clicking "<a
              href="https://boatlifestyle.shiprocket.co/"
              style="font-weight: bold"
              >Track your Order</a
            >" at the top right corner.
          </p>

          <p>
            If you are an existing user you can simply log in to your account
            and track your current and past order details. However, if you
            haven’t made an account and has signed in as a guest user - we
            advise you to create your account with the same guest user mail id.
          </p>

          <p>
            *Please note, that it can take some time before the tracking
            information is uploaded.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="section--heading">Exchanges</h2>
    <div class="faqs-section">
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">When will I receive my refund?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Once we have received your return shipment in our warehouse, we will
            send you an email confirming receipt of the package. We will refund
            the value of your returned items within 30 days upon receiving the
            return package.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">
          I used my guest order id to log in but that was not being accepted. I
          tried to change my password as well but could not go through with
          that. Why?
        </p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            In order to log in you have to register on the boAt website and
            become a user. Create your account by going to
            <a
              href="https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/account/register"
              style="font-weight: bold"
              >https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/account/register</a
            >. Use the same email id that you entered when placing your order on
            the boAt store.
          </p>
          <p>
            Once you create an account you will be able to log in and view all
            relevant information about your past order(s).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
