    <h2 class="my-5 product--specific">Product Related FAQs</h2>
    <h2 class="section--heading">Airdopes</h2>
    <div class="faqs-section">
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">What to do if one of the Airdopes stop working?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>Simply reset your device.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">What to do if the Airdopes are not charging?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Keep the Airdopes aside and plug in your charging case for 15
            minutes. Now put the Airdopes back in the charging case.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">How can we pause and play tracks?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Single tap the capacitive touch control on either earbud to play or
            pause a song.
          </p>
          <p>
            boAt Airdopes are a feature-packed collection with a host of
            intuitive features that allow one to control music seamlessly.
            Please refer to the instruction manual to learn how to enjoy its
            features completely.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">Can we take calls on boAt Airdopes?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Yes, a single press on the multi-function button allows the user to
            accept and reject calls easily.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">Can I use any adapter to charge the Airdopes?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>Yes, you can use any adapter to charge your Airdopes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">
          Are all Airdopes waterproof and sweat resistant?
        </p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Yes, Airdopes generally come with IPX Dust and Water Resistance
            technology. You can use it for your workouts or carry them along on
            long trips.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">What is the use of the charging case?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            The charging case is ergonomically designed to be portable and
            lightweight. You can carry your in-ear earbuds around while they’re
            being charged in the case.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">
          Are Airdopes compatible with iPhones and Android phones?
        </p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Yes, Airdopes are fully compatible with iPhones and Android devices.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">How can I connect with Google and Siri?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Simply double-tap to connect with Google & Siri and activate the
            voice assistant. Please refer to the manual for further
            instructions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="section--heading">Rockerz</h2>
    <div class="faqs-section">
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">What to do when one side stops working?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>Simply reset your Rockerz device.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">
