    <h2 class="section--heading">Bassheads</h2>
    <div class="faqs-section">
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">
          Can we accept calls? Are they good for calls, meetings, and work from
          home?
        </p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Single press on the multi-function button to easily accept and
            reject calls. Bassheads are designed for clarity and comfort during
            meetings and important calls.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">Do they have noise cancellation?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>Bassheads come with passive noise cancellation for clear sound.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-block">
        <p class="accordion">Do they have a dedicated microphone?</p>
        <div class="panel">
          <p>
            Yes, Bassheads earphones have a dedicated mic perfect for calls and
            recording.
          </p>
